# --- dashdown build outputs (static export from `dashdown build`) ---
/dist-site/

# --- tooling/ (release-only Node asset build) ---
tooling/node_modules/
tooling/package-lock.json
tooling/npm-debug.log*

# --- Local DB / data scratch ---
*.duckdb
*.duckdb.wal
*.db-journal

